@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gotqli(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.71 + v0 + 0.74) - v1) - wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.68)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.36)) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.35) * tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
